room_title: Escape room "Escape the Legend of Luna Park" by Electric City Escape in Scranton
room_description: Luna Park at night was magical with its strings of lights all around, fantastical rides, and lively music, but as with all things Luna Park had its share of secrets. Local legend has it, that the fortune teller, the “Maid of Mystery” had a treasure within the park. You and your friends sneak into the park late one night, with just an hour to closing time, to find this treasure for yourselves. Unfortunately, on this particular night, you’re not the only ones with a secret plan! Better move quickly!
